536
00:40:10,541 --> 00:40:12,208
Ke mana perginya kapal itu?

537
00:40:12,791 --> 00:40:15,458
Entahlah. Mereka mematikan GPS.

538
00:40:15,541 --> 00:40:18,750
<i>Begitu mereka tak menemukan rute kita,</i>

539
00:40:18,833 --> 00:40:21,333
<i>mereka akan mendapati kejadian aneh lain.</i>

540
00:40:22,875 --> 00:40:24,416
Penculikan di laut.

