760
00:54:51,916 --> 00:54:54,833
- Bagaimana di Denmark?
- Pertukaran yang indah.

761
00:55:13,041 --> 00:55:14,041
Keluar!

762
00:55:20,916 --> 00:55:25,875
Ingot di truk itu terbuat
dari kuningan berlapis emas.

763
00:55:26,875 --> 00:55:28,416
Sudah kuperingatkan.

764
00:55:29,000 --> 00:55:30,166
Suárez, Cañizo, bidik!

765
00:55:30,250 --> 00:55:31,083
Bidik!

766
00:55:35,583 --> 00:55:36,541
Tamayo, tunggu.

767
00:55:36,625 --> 00:55:40,833
Ingot itu telah menghentikan
bencana utang.

768
00:55:45,375 --> 00:55:47,666
Bukankah kau Robin Hood?

